#: prime/templates/prime/about.html:478
msgid ""
"A learning platform built for curious minds — where students grow through "
"structured practice, mentorship from expert masters, and a community that "
"pushes boundaries together."
msgstr ""
"Qiziquvchan onglar uchun qurilgan ta'lim platformasi — o'quvchilar tizimli "
"mashqlar, mutaxassis ustodlarning mentorlik va chegaralarni kengaytiruvchi "
"jamoa orqali rivojlanadigan joy."

#: prime/templates/prime/about.html:482 prime/templates/prime/help.html:363
#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:883
