msgstr "Bepul boshlash"

#: prime/templates/prime/about.html:502
msgid "Clear Goal"
msgstr "Aniq maqsad"

#: prime/templates/prime/about.html:506
msgid "Every Learner"
msgstr "Har bir o'quvchi"

#: prime/templates/prime/about.html:513
msgid "Our Mission"
msgstr "Bizning maqsadimiz"

#: prime/templates/prime/about.html:514
msgid "Sharpening minds,"
msgstr "Onglarni charxlash,"

#: prime/templates/prime/about.html:514
msgid "one question at a time."
msgstr "har bir savol bilan."

#: prime/templates/prime/about.html:517
msgid ""
"Prime Point was founded on a simple belief: the best way to build a strong "
"mind is through deliberate, structured practice. We connect passionate "
"learners with expert masters and give them the tools to grow — at their own "
"pace, on their own terms."
msgstr ""
"Prime Point oddiy bir e'tiqod asosida tashkil etilgan: kuchli ong qurishning "
"eng yaxshi yo'li — maqsadli, tizimli mashq. Biz ishtiyoqli o'quvchilarni "
"mutaxassis ustodlar bilan bog'laymiz va ularga o'sish uchun qurollar beramiz "
"— o'z sur'atlarida, o'z shartlarida."

#: prime/templates/prime/about.html:520
msgid ""
"We are not just a quiz app. We are a full learning ecosystem — from homework "
"assignments to live discussion, from beginner practices to expert-level "
"challenges."
msgstr ""
"Biz shunchaki viktorina ilovasi emasmiz. Biz to'liq ta'lim ekotizimizmiz — "
"uy vazifalaridan jonli muhokamagacha, boshlang'ich mashqlardan ekspert "
"darajasidagi qiyinchiliklargacha."

#: prime/templates/prime/about.html:527
msgid "Deliberate Practice"
msgstr "Maqsadli mashq"

#: prime/templates/prime/about.html:528
msgid "Targeted, measurable improvement every session"
msgstr "Har bir mashg'ulotda aniq va o'lchovli taraqqiyot"

#: prime/templates/prime/about.html:534
msgid "Expert Mentorship"
msgstr "Mutaxassis mentorlik"

#: prime/templates/prime/about.html:535
msgid "Learn directly from masters in their field"
msgstr "O'z sohasidagi ustodlardan bevosita o'rganing"

#: prime/templates/prime/about.html:541
msgid "Visible Progress"
msgstr "Ko'rinadigan taraqqiyot"

#: prime/templates/prime/about.html:542
msgid "Track your rank from Novice to Grandmaster"
msgstr "Yangilikdan Grandmastergacha darajangizni kuzating"

#: prime/templates/prime/about.html:548
msgid "Community Learning"
msgstr "Jamoaviy ta'lim"

#: prime/templates/prime/about.html:549
msgid "Discuss, debate, and grow alongside peers"
msgstr "Tengdoshlar bilan muhokama qiling va birgalikda rivojlaning"

#: prime/templates/prime/about.html:557
msgid "What We Offer"
msgstr "Nima taklif etamiz"

#: prime/templates/prime/about.html:558
msgid "Everything you need to level up."
msgstr "Darajangizni oshirish uchun hamma narsa."

#: prime/templates/prime/about.html:565
msgid ""
"Hundreds of curated practice sessions across subjects and difficulty levels. "
"Filter by topic, master, or level — and track your score every attempt."
msgstr ""
"Turli fanlar va qiyinlik darajalari bo'yicha yuzlab tanlangan mashq "
"sessiyalari. Mavzu, ustod yoki daraja bo'yicha filtrlang — va har bir "
"urinishda natijangizni kuzating."

#: prime/templates/prime/about.html:569 prime/templates/prime/help.html:588
msgid "Homework System"
msgstr "Uy vazifasi tizimi"

#: prime/templates/prime/about.html:570
msgid ""
"Masters assign targeted practice as homework to individual students or "
"groups. Deadlines, auto-grading, and submission tracking built in."
msgstr ""
"Ustodlar alohida o'quvchilarga yoki guruhlarga uy vazifasi sifatida maqsadli "
"mashqlar tayinlaydi. Muddatlar, avtomatik baholash va topshiriqlarni "
"kuzatish o'rnatilgan."

#: prime/templates/prime/about.html:574
msgid "Master Profiles"
msgstr "Ustod profillari"

#: prime/templates/prime/about.html:575
msgid ""
"Follow experts in your field. Each master curates their own practice library "
"and can guide their students through structured learning paths."
msgstr ""
"Sohangizdagi mutaxassislarni kuzating. Har bir ustod o'zining mashqlar "
"kutubxonasini boshqaradi va tizimli o'quv yo'llari orqali o'quvchilarini "
"yo'naltiradi."

#: prime/templates/prime/about.html:579 prime/templates/prime/help.html:681
msgid "Discussion Forum"
msgstr "Muhokama forumi"

#: prime/templates/prime/about.html:580
msgid ""
"Engage with the community — ask questions, share insights, vote on answers, "
"and learn from conversations that go beyond the practice sheet."
msgstr ""
"Jamoa bilan muloqot qiling — savollar bering, fikrlar ulashing, javoblarga "
"ovoz bering va mashq varag'idan tashqariga chiqadigan suhbatlardan o'rganing."

#: prime/templates/prime/about.html:584 prime/templates/prime/help.html:711
msgid "Rank System"
msgstr "Daraja tizimi"

#: prime/templates/prime/about.html:585
msgid ""
"Earn points through practice and climb from Novice to Grandmaster. Your rank "
"reflects your dedication — and motivates you to keep going."
msgstr ""
"Mashq orqali ball to'plang va Yangilikdan Grandmastergacha ko'tariling. "
"Darajangiz fidoyiligingizni aks ettiradi — va davom etishga undaydi."

#: prime/templates/prime/about.html:590
msgid ""
"Masters see exactly where each student struggles — question by question, "
"choice by choice. Targeted feedback becomes effortless."
msgstr ""
"Ustodlar har bir o'quvchining qayerda qiynalayotganini aniq ko'radi — savol "
"savoldan, tanlov tanlovdan. Maqsadli fikr-mulohaza berish osonlashadi."

#: prime/templates/prime/about.html:596
msgid "How It Works"
msgstr "Qanday ishlaydi"

#: prime/templates/prime/about.html:597
msgid "Simple steps. Real results."
msgstr "Oddiy qadamlar. Haqiqiy natijalar."

#: prime/templates/prime/about.html:603
msgid "Create your account"
msgstr "Hisobingizni yarating"

#: prime/templates/prime/about.html:604
msgid ""
