msgstr "Ustodni kuzating"

#: prime/templates/prime/about.html:609
msgid ""
"Browse expert masters and follow the ones whose subjects align with your "
"goals."
msgstr ""
"Mutaxassis ustodlarni ko'rib chiqing va maqsadlaringizga mos keladiganlarini "
"kuzating."

#: prime/templates/prime/about.html:613
msgid "Practice & Submit"
msgstr "Mashq qiling va topshiring"

#: prime/templates/prime/about.html:614
msgid ""
"Take timed or open-ended practice sessions. Submit homework assigned by your "
"masters."
msgstr ""
"Vaqt chegaralangan yoki ochiq mashq sessiyalarini bajaring. Ustodlaringiz "
"tomonidan berilgan uy vazifalarini topshiring."

#: prime/templates/prime/about.html:618
msgid "Review & Grow"
msgstr "Tahlil qiling va rivojlaning"

#: prime/templates/prime/about.html:619
msgid ""
"See detailed feedback on every answer. Improve your weak points. Rise "
"through the ranks."
msgstr ""
"Har bir javob uchun batafsil fikr-mulohaza ko'ring. Zaif tomonlaringizni "
"yaxshilang. Darajangizni oshiring."

