#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:359
msgid ""
"Everything you need to know about using Prime Point — whether you are a "
"student looking to grow, a master building your classroom, or an educational "
"center onboarding your team."
msgstr ""
"Prime Pointdan foydalanish haqida bilishingiz kerak bo'lgan hamma narsa — "
"o'sishni istagan o'quvchi, darsxonasini qurayotgan ustod yoki jamoasini "
"o'rgatayotgan ta'lim markazi uchun."

