msgid "Quick Start"
msgstr "Tezkor boshlash"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:374
msgid "Up and running in four steps"
msgstr "To'rt qadamda ishga kiring"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:380
msgid "Create an Account"
msgstr "Hisob yaratish"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:381
msgid "Register for free. No payment required — just a username and password."
msgstr ""
"Bepul ro'yxatdan o'ting. To'lov talab qilinmaydi — faqat foydalanuvchi nomi "
"va parol."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:386
msgid ""
"Go to your Profile and use the Masters selector to choose the educators you "
"want to follow."
msgstr ""
"Profilingizga o'ting va kuzatmoqchi bo'lgan o'qituvchilarni tanlash uchun "
"Ustodlar tanlagichidan foydalaning."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:390
msgid "Take a Practice"
msgstr "Mashqni topshirish"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:391
msgid ""
"Choose a timed or open-ended practice set and submit your answers to earn "
"points."
msgstr ""
"Vaqtli yoki ochiq mashqlar to'plamini tanlang va ball olish uchun "
"javoblaringizni yuboring."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:395
msgid "Rise in Rank"
msgstr "Darajada ko'tarilish"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:396
msgid "Accumulate points and climb from Novice all the way to Grandmaster."
msgstr "Ball to'plang va Yangilikdan Grandmastergacha ko'tariling."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:403
msgid "For Educators"
msgstr "O'qituvchilar uchun"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:404
msgid "Becoming a Master"
msgstr "Ustod bo'lish"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:407
msgid ""
"Masters are approved educators who create content, manage students, and run "
"classrooms. Becoming a Master is a straightforward three-step process."
msgstr ""
"Ustodlar — kontent yaratadiagan, o'quvchilarni boshqaradigan va "
"darsxonalarni yuritadigan tasdiqlangan o'qituvchilar. Ustod bo'lish uch "
"bosqichli oddiy jarayon."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:416
msgid "Submit Your Application"
msgstr "Arizangizni yuboring"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:417
msgid ""
"Visit the Masters page and click 'Become a Master'. Fill in your name, "
"subject, and a short description."
msgstr ""
"Ustodlar sahifasiga o'ting va 'Ustod bo'lish' tugmasini bosing. Ismingiz, "
"faning va qisqa tavsifni to'ldiring."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:423
msgid "Await Admin Approval"
msgstr "Admin tasdiqlashini kuting"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:424
msgid ""
"An admin reviews your profile. Your dashboard will show a pending badge "
"while the review is in progress."
msgstr ""
"Admin profilingizni ko'rib chiqadi. Ko'rib chiqish davomida boshqaruv "
"panelingizda kutish belgisi ko'rsatiladi."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:430
msgid "Unlock Full Master Tools"
msgstr "Barcha Ustod vositalarini oching"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:431
msgid ""
"Once approved, you can create practices, assign homework, publish tutorials, "
"and run private classrooms."
msgstr ""
"Tasdiqlanganingizdan so'ng mashqlar yaratish, uy vazifalari tayinlash, "
"darsliklar chop etish va xususiy darsxonalar yuritish mumkin."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:437
msgid "Apply Now"
msgstr "Hozir ariza bering"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:443
msgid "Application Flow"
msgstr "Ariza jarayoni"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:446
msgid "Fill in the Master application form"
msgstr "Ustod ariza shaklini to'ldiring"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:450
msgid "Pending admin review"
msgstr "Admin ko'rib chiqmoqda"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:455
msgid "Approved — all tools unlocked"
msgstr "Tasdiqlandi — barcha vositalar ochildi"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:456
msgid "Approved"
msgstr "Tasdiqlangan"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:464
msgid "Master Capabilities"
msgstr "Ustod imkoniyatlari"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:465
msgid "What Masters Can Do"
msgstr "Ustodlar nima qila oladi"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:468
msgid ""
"Approved Masters have a full suite of teaching and management tools at their "
"disposal."
msgstr ""
"Tasdiqlangan Ustodlarda o'qitish va boshqarish uchun to'liq vositalar "
"to'plami mavjud."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:474
msgid "Create Practices"
msgstr "Mashqlar yaratish"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:475
msgid ""
"Build multiple-choice question sets with difficulty levels (easy / medium / "
"hard), time limits, pass scores, and max attempt caps."
msgstr ""
"Qiyinlik darajasi (oson / o'rta / qiyin), vaqt chegarasi, o'tish bali va "
"maksimal urinishlar bilan test savollari to'plamlari tuzing."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:479
msgid "Manage Students"
msgstr "O'quvchilarni boshqarish"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:480
msgid ""
"View everyone who follows you. Remove students from your roster and organise "
"them into named groups for bulk operations."
msgstr ""
"Sizi kuzatayotgan barcha kishilarni ko'ring. O'quvchilarni ro'yxatdan "
"o'chiring va ommaviy amallar uchun ularni nomlangan guruhlarga joylashtiring."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:484
msgid "Create Groups"
msgstr "Guruhlar yaratish"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:485
msgid ""
"Group students by class, level, or any criteria. Assign homework to a whole "
"group with a single action instead of individually."
msgstr ""
"O'quvchilarni sinf, daraja yoki boshqa mezonlar bo'yicha guruhlang. Har biri "
"alohida o'rniga bitta amal bilan butun guruhga uy vazifasi tayinlang."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:489
msgid "Assign Homework"
msgstr "Uy vazifasi tayinlash"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:490
msgid ""
"Link any practice to individual students or groups, add notes, and set an "
"optional deadline. Track status — Pending, Submitted, or Graded."
msgstr ""
"Har qanday mashqni alohida o'quvchilarga yoki guruhlarga bog'lang, izoh "
"qo'shing va ixtiyoriy muddat belgilang. Holat — Kutilmoqda, Topshirilgan "
"yoki Baholangan."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:494
msgid "Write Tutorials"
msgstr "Darsliklar yozish"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:495
msgid ""
"Publish rich-text articles with a category, thumbnail, and linked practices. "
"Students can like or dislike your tutorials."
msgstr ""
"Kategoriya, eskiz va bog'langan mashqlar bilan boy matnli maqolalar chop "
"eting. O'quvchilar darsliklaringizni yoqtirishi yoki yoqtirmasligi mumkin."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:499
msgid "Run Classrooms"
msgstr "Darsxonalarni yuritish"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:500
msgid ""
"Create private classrooms with structured lessons. Attach practices, "
"homework, and tutorials to each lesson. Host a classroom-level discussion."
msgstr ""
"Tuzilgan darslar bilan xususiy darsxonalar yarating. Har bir darsga "
"mashqlar, uy vazifalari va darsliklarni biriktiring. Darsxona darajasida "
"muhokama o'tkazing."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:504
msgid "Generate Certificates"
msgstr "Sertifikatlar yaratish"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:505
msgid ""
"Issue printable certificates to your students directly from your Master "
"profile page — no third-party tool needed."
msgstr ""
"O'quvchilaringizga Ustod profili sahifangizdan to'g'ridan-to'g'ri chop "
"etiladigan sertifikatlar bering — uchinchi tomon vositasi shart emas."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:512
msgid "For Students"
msgstr "O'quvchilar uchun"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:513
msgid "Student Guide"
msgstr "O'quvchi qo'llanmasi"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:519
msgid "How to Choose and Follow a Master"
msgstr "Ustod qanday tanlanadi va obuna qilinadi"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:520
msgid ""
"Browse the Masters list to see all approved educators. Click any master to "
"view their profile, subject, average student score, and the practices they "
"have published."
msgstr ""
"Barcha tasdiqlangan o'qituvchilarni ko'rish uchun Ustodlar ro'yxatiga "
"o'ting. Profilini, fanini, o'quvchilarning o'rtacha balini va chop etilgan "
"mashqlarini ko'rish uchun istalgan ustodga bosing."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:522
msgid "Go to your Profile page after logging in."
msgstr "Kirganingizdan so'ng Profil sahifangizga o'ting."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:523
msgid ""
"Scroll to the Masters section and use the selector to add the masters you "
"want to follow."
msgstr ""
"Ustodlar bo'limiga o'ting va kuzatmoqchi bo'lgan ustodlarni qo'shish uchun "
"tanlagichdan foydalaning."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:524
msgid ""
"Save your profile. The master's practices and homework will now be "
"accessible to you."
msgstr ""
"Profilingizni saqlang. Ustodning mashqlari va uy vazifalari endi sizga ochiq "
"bo'ladi."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:525
msgid "You can follow multiple masters at the same time."
msgstr "Bir vaqtning o'zida bir nechta ustodga obuna bo'lish mumkin."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:526
msgid "Remove a master from your selector at any time to unfollow."
msgstr ""
"Obunani bekor qilish uchun istalgan vaqt tanlagichdan ustodni o'chiring."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:531
msgid "How it looks"
msgstr "Qanday ko'rinadi"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:534
msgid "Browse Masters page"
msgstr "Ustodlar sahifasini ko'rish"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:538
msgid "View master profile & practices"
msgstr "Ustod profili va mashqlarini ko'rish"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:542
msgid "Open your Profile → Masters selector"
msgstr "Profil → Ustodlar tanlagichini oching"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:546
msgid "Save — now enrolled as a student"
msgstr "Saqlash — endi o'quvchi sifatida ro'yxatdan o'tdingiz"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:547
msgid "Done"
msgstr "Bajarildi"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:555
msgid "Feature Guide"
msgstr "Xususiyatlar bo'yicha qo'llanma"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:556
msgid "Platform Features"
msgstr "Platforma xususiyatlari"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:562
msgid "Practice System"
msgstr "Mashqlar tizimi"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:563
msgid ""
"Practices are the core of Prime Point. Each practice is a set of multiple-"
"choice questions created by a master. Masters configure exactly how students "
"experience each practice."
msgstr ""
"Mashqlar Prime Pointning asosi. Har bir mashq ustod tomonidan yaratilgan "
"ko'p tanlovli savollar to'plami. Ustodlar o'quvchilar har bir mashqni qanday "
"boshdan kechirishini aniq sozlaydi."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:565
msgid "Three difficulty levels: Easy, Medium, Hard."
msgstr "Uchta qiyinlik darajasi: Oson, O'rta, Qiyin."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:566
msgid ""
"Optional time limit — the timer counts down and auto-submits when it expires."
msgstr ""
"Ixtiyoriy vaqt chegarasi — taymer orqaga hisoblaydi va muddati tugaganda "
"avtomatik topshiradi."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:567
msgid "Pass score threshold — you must reach this percentage to pass."
msgstr "O'tish bali chegarasi — o'tish uchun ushbu foizga yetishingiz kerak."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:568
msgid ""
"Max attempts cap — masters can limit how many times a student can retry."
msgstr ""
"Maksimal urinishlar chegarasi — ustodlar o'quvchi necha marta qayta "
"urinishini cheklashi mumkin."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:569
msgid ""
"Show-answers-after option — correct answers are revealed once the attempt is "
"completed."
msgstr ""
"To'g'ri javoblarni ko'rsatish opsiyasi — urinish tugagandan so'ng to'g'ri "
"javoblar ochiladi."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:570
msgid ""
"Free and available-for-all flags — masters can open a practice to the entire "
"platform."
msgstr ""
"Bepul va hammaga ochiq bayroqlar — ustodlar mashqni butun platforma uchun "
"ochaoladi."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:575
msgid "Practice Metadata"
msgstr "Mashq ma'lumotlari"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:579
msgid "Max Attempts"
msgstr "Maks. urinishlar"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:589
msgid ""
"Masters link a practice to a homework assignment and push it directly to "
"students or groups. Students complete the linked practice to submit the "
"homework."
msgstr ""
"Ustodlar mashqni uy vazifasiga bog'laydi va to'g'ridan-to'g'ri o'quvchilarga "
"yoki guruhlarga yuboradi. O'quvchilar uy vazifasini topshirish uchun "
"bog'langan mashqni bajaradi."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:591
msgid ""
"Create homework: give it a title, optional notes, a linked practice, and an "
"optional due date."
msgstr ""
"Uy vazifasini yarating: sarlavha, ixtiyoriy izoh, bog'langan mashq va "
"ixtiyoriy topshirish muddatini kiriting."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:592
msgid "Assign to individual students or to an entire group in one step."
msgstr "Bir qadamda alohida o'quvchilarga yoki butun guruhga tayinlang."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:593
msgid ""
"Student completes the practice → homework status moves to Submitted "
"automatically."
msgstr ""
"O'quvchi mashqni bajaradi → uy vazifasi holati avtomatik ravishda "
"Topshirilgan'ga o'tadi."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:594
msgid "Master grades the submission and can leave written feedback."
msgstr "Ustod topshiriqni baholaydi va yozma fikr bildirishi mumkin."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:595
msgid "Track per-student status from the homework detail view."
msgstr ""
"Uy vazifasi tafsilotlari ko'rinishidan har bir o'quvchi holatini kuzating."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:607
msgid "Assignment Overview"
msgstr "Topshiriq ko'rinishi"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:608
msgid "Group: Advanced Class"
msgstr "Guruh: Ilg'or sinf"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:608
msgid "students"
msgstr "o'quvchi"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:609
msgid "Practice: Grammar Test 3"
msgstr "Mashq: Grammatika testi 3"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:610
msgid "Due date"
msgstr "Topshirish muddati"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:619
msgid "Tutorial System"
msgstr "Darsliklar tizimi"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:620
msgid ""
"Tutorials are long-form rich-text articles written by masters. They can "
"include images, formatted text, and links to related practices — turning a "
"lesson into an interactive experience."
msgstr ""
"Darsliklar — ustodlar tomonidan yozilgan boy matnli uzun maqolalar. Ular "
"rasmlar, formatlangan matn va tegishli mashqlarga havolalarni o'z ichiga "
"olishi mumkin — darsni interaktiv tajribaga aylantiradi."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:622
msgid "Categories: Mathematics, Korean, Programming, English, Other."
msgstr "Kategoriyalar: Matematika, Koreys, Dasturlash, Ingliz, Boshqa."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:623
msgid "Read time is estimated automatically from the word count."
msgstr "O'qish vaqti so'zlar sonidan avtomatik hisoblanadi."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:624
msgid "Students can like or dislike a tutorial to give the author feedback."
msgstr ""
"O'quvchilar muallifga fikr bildirish uchun darslikni yoqtirishi yoki "
"yoqtirmasligi mumkin."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:625
msgid ""
"Link any number of practices to a tutorial so students can test themselves "
"immediately."
msgstr ""
"O'quvchilar darhol o'zlarini sinab ko'rishi uchun darslikka istalgan "
"miqdordagi mashqlarni bog'lang."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:626
msgid ""
"View count is tracked so masters can see which tutorials are most popular."
msgstr ""
"Ko'rishlar soni kuzatiladi, shuning uchun ustodlar qaysi darsliklar "
"mashhurligini ko'rishi mumkin."

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:631
msgid "Tutorial Card"
msgstr "Darslik kartasi"

