msgstr "Eng yaxshi javob qabul qilindi"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:710
msgid "Progression"
msgstr "Rivojlanish"

#: prime/templates/prime/help.html:714
msgid ""
"Your rank is calculated from the total points earned across all completed "
"practices. The higher your score on each attempt, the more points you "
"receive."
msgstr ""
"Darajangiz barcha bajarilgan mashqlar bo'yicha to'plangan umumiy ballar "
"asosida hisoblanadi. Har bir urinishdagi balingiz qanchalik yuqori bo'lsa, "
"shunchalik ko'proq ball olasiz."

